      "id": "insight-managed-platforms-are-retention-loops",
      "title": "Managed services create retention through operating burden reduction",
      "summary": "The domain brief frames public cloud as programmable technology building blocks, but durable adoption depends on managed databases, app runtimes, analytics, AI, eventing, observability, and support becoming cheaper to operate than equivalent self-managed stacks.",
      "implications": [
        "Track managed-service attach by workload cohort.",
        "Connect developer activation metrics to support deflection and incident-rate metrics."
      ],
