      "id": "insight-governance-is-a-product-not-a-back-office-function",
      "title": "Enterprise cloud governance is a product surface",
      "summary": "Enterprise and regulated customers cannot scale cloud adoption if identity, network, policy, encryption, audit, and cost controls remain external review processes. The product must make safe defaults and evidence generation part of provisioning.",
      "implications": [
        "Landing-zone quality should be measured as product activation quality.",
        "Security and FinOps operators need workflow surfaces, not only raw telemetry."
      ],
