      "summary": "Enterprises do not adopt cloud as a greenfield-only motion. Legacy modernization, private connectivity, identity federation, disaster recovery, and hybrid operating models decide migration throughput and long-term credibility.",
      "implications": [
        "Migration factory, backup/recovery, virtual networking, support, and governance should be planned together.",
        "Discoveries should explicitly test blockers in legacy dependency mapping and cutover readiness."
