      "title": "Commitment discounts are a retention product, not only a pricing tactic",
      "summary": "AWS Savings Plans, Azure savings plans, and Google Cloud committed use discounts all exchange lower prices for one- or three-year usage or spend commitments. That makes renewal quality depend on recommendation accuracy, commitment utilization, and customer confidence that future workloads can still evolve.",
